videos.headline: Collier responds to 'overrated' chant by sinking FT, blocking a shot
videos.description: While Texas' Charli Collier is at the foul line vs. Bradley, an "overrated" chant comes from the stands. Collier subsequently sinks her free throw and blocks Tatum Koenig's shot on the other end.
